	(text "Tsumikoro TMC2130 Dual Stepper Controller — rev 0.1\n\nMCU: STM32G071G8U6 (UFQFPN-28, same as firmware/tsumikoro-ministepper target)\nLogic supply: 3.3V from TPS54061 PSU sub-sheet (sized for ~100mA logic + 2x TMC2130 VCC_IO)\nMotor supply: VPP — from bus V+ (via JBUS1/JBUS2 pin 1) or external JPWR DC jack,\n             Schottky-OR'd so whichever source is highest wins.\nSense resistors: 0.1 ohm 1% 1210 (2x per TMC) -> ~1.6A RMS max with VFS=325mV\nRS-485 bus: USART2 on PA2/PA3 (no SYSCFG remap needed unlike servo's G030)\n\nComponents placed but NOT wired — wiring pending in KiCad editor."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20 20 0)
